reviews.review_text: I don t like the squishmallow McFlurry.

I love McDonalds with all my heart. From the moment I first stepped in, it was like an epiphany had happened for me. McDonalds is my place of clarity, worship, and love. Their food is like a blessing to your body. Healing, passion. I will come here for every meal to pay tribute to the fallen ice cream machines, and others who work to improve this world. Kid-friendliness: Grimace shake
This Mcdonald s is the best one in Metro Vancouver. Food was very fresh and delicious. The service was amazing and so were the workers! I 100% recommend to come to this Mcdonald s location.

Good food for quick grab,friendly staff,clean restaurant,good location with lots of parking :) Vegetarian options: Available and can ask staff to modify orders according to food restrictions or preferences. Dietary restrictions: Lots of choices,easy to read menus and staff always available and knowledgeable about dietary restrictions or food preferences :) Parking: Lots of free parking sorrounding the restaurant Kid-friendliness: Delicious /fair and good price of food for kids and staff always smile and friendly to customers. Wheelchair accessibility: I don t use wheelchair but store is very accessible and safe for cane,walkers or wheelchairs users/customers.

Great drive through McDonald s experience. Quick, efficient and friendly staff. My egg McMuffin with no bacon, added lettuce and tomato was excellent. The hash brown was fresh and hot, likewise for the coffee. I have always had a great experience at this location and it continues to today. Thanks folks!
Best made Big Mac I ve ever had since 1970
The only negative point that is not related to this McDonalds is the location. I had a hard time to getting in this plaza and getting out. You must take a big detour to reach there.

The staff at this location are great. The service is fast, friendly and accurate for the most part. I was given a wrong coffee once and a few days later when I mentioned it to a manager they offered to give me a coffee to make right the wrong order previously. I know their job is not as easy as some people think it is as I was an assistant manager for McDonalds before. Keep up the good work guys you a credit to the fast food industry.
Took them about 26 minutes to make food. Its great because i had to go use restroom and food was still warm. I am loving it!
One of the best McDonald s we have ever been to in the world!! Typical McDonald s food, but had lots of unique options with the donuts, drinks, and kit kat McFlurry! Loved this Canadian experience!
The employees here are very personable. They dont always have what you want. But their happy demeanor makes up for it. Still awesome Food : 3/5 | Service

It was great and quick service, you can enjoy delicious drinks and snacks here, you should definitely visit here Vegetarian options: If you are a vegetarian or vegan, snacks are not for you, but you can enjoy several drinks here in mc cafe. Parking: Easy parking Kid-friendliness: Yes its kids friendly I can see cartoon themed chairs for kids. Theyll love it.

Great customer service and awesome support from manager! My daughter and her friends were very happy and excited to have her birthday party there! Fantastic memories of her birthday! Thank you everyone for your kindness and support

The psycho drive thru cashier pushed down all my drink lid buttons. Way to take the fun out of my drink, LADY! The cashier who took my money was very friendly though. It s actually quite a fancy restaurant. 5 stars

Love the McFlurry, I like the burger, I like the soda and the seats, But I would mostly eat outside at home. I dont really care about the time of my order cause I dont have anything to do. But Bruh that one Vanilla drink IS Ooooo So good MM.
Great! Right beside the movie theater too
The best service. I ordered an extra patty for my puppy and the manager came to the window and made sure to ask if I wanted it without seasoning!     Also, during peek Lunch time!  Thank you staff!
Always clean, abiding by all the chain standards with a Convenient location, with a easy access to the highway , with plenty of electric vehicles charging stations.

Went through the drive-thru today and ordered 2 sausage McMuffins with double cheese. Got asked to go around to curbside, no problem. Waited quite a long time  but I ll be damned if those weren t the best two McMuffins of my life. Perfectly toasted, crispy hot, cheese melty but not stuck to the paper, they were delicious. Well done and thank you! Will be back for more.

The ladies behind the counter were very polite, kind and so nice. I got my daughter a meal. The fries were crispy and fresh, the burger had fresh crispy onions, pickles and it was delicious. Thank you for making my daughter happy
Everything is good, staff are nice and polite. Parking is not much space, due to construction next door of new TnT Supermarket. The driving area and parking is limited.
First time trying the McGriddle...yum!
Best customer service i have ever had at this location. The staff was very friendly especially the young women named Pawan. I ll highly recommend this McDonald s!

Whenever I visit this location the food is always fresh. I have never had fresh mcdonalds food even when you ask other places they say they will make it fresh but the line cooks just warm it up in the fryer. This Mcdonalds in particular always has the drive through figured out and very rarely do they make you wait for your order. Would recommend.

I can t believe I am giving a 5 stars review to a McDonald s, for the first time while doing deliveries, I have been treated nicely by someone working at McDonald s. My order wasn t ready, but the staff let me know they are working on it, showed a sense of urgency and even offered me a free drink cause its taking them a while, damn, mind blown, finally, a McDonald s I like..... shout out to Harpreet, best McDonald s employee, I have seen so far.....

I visit this location almost every morning on my way to work and I have to say the staff is just top notch.  They are always soo friendly and always have a smile on their faces.  They know my order before I even finish ordering.  Just wanted to commend them on their great customer service.
The fries here are phenomenal. Its like each order is made to order. With a side of bbq sauce or a little bit of mayo. Heaven!

Always fast service at this location, very little wait time and rarely have an issue with receiving the proper order. The only downside is the amount of parking accessable for bigger vehicles, other than that Ive never had a bad experience at this location

reviews.reviewer_name: Renata Steele Vancouver / Kelowna area (Realtor Vancouver BC)
reviews.review_text: Friendly service, clean restaurant, my daughter loves playing in the play place. Great table service option. Food came quickly. The fries were perfectly salted, love the big mac

One of the best McDonalds around. Super fast service, very few mistakes made, and very friendly staff. I work just up the road and we eat here often because of how much better this place is compared to other local fast food spots.
Saw a new girl employee working here named Diksha , shes so nice ,I send her back two times to grab extra straws and napkins for my curbside order , shes so fast and so polite , overall good food
Like any other McDonald s out there. No complaints. Service is fast.
Standard McDonald s, they gave us free fries for waiting, because the pies for 15 minutes
Was a well run place a perfect order and tastes great...
Totally upgraded from last time I was at a McDs. You can order yourself at the board right inside the door, then you order is called when its ready. I like personal service though

Clean and fast service as per usual with McDonalds. The only thing I can find wrong with this location is the funky drive-thru and I realize that they had to build within the given space but its so awkward. Other than that its a smaller location but typical eatary.

Everyone love McDonalds...but unfortunately Muslims... Indus...Jews and vegetarians dont really get to enjoy it...because grills use for bacon and other meats are all cooked on same grills...not making it kolsher or halal for them... McDonalds are millionaires...they should put efforts in finding a solution for all ethnic of any background feel welcome and be part of their family...if u have time to rebuild to install table with number and order box stations for customers... shouldnt u have grills for beef separate from grills for bacon...and use vegetable oils for all ingredients...all ur workers should equally respect changing gloves according to what their cooking...imagine if doctors never washed their hands or never changed glove for each patient he sees...how sick the world would get... McDonalds serve thousands and millions a day throughout the world... McDonalds like a mother preparing meals for her family...would she give none caring meals that might not be agreeable with each individual needs...trust me Im a mom...I have to watch out for allergies...one wants to be vegetarian...one loves more beef...the other wants chicken...no pork families have rights to be welcome at McDonalds...so make it happen...thx
The staff is so kind and the hamburger is delicious.
Weekend morning drive thru is always on point. Excellent!
This is the most welcoming McDonalds restaurant Ive seen in Vancouver
Amazing service. The Fijian kid at the cash counter was super polite and friendly. Best service Ive ever had at a McDs.
Good fast service, eating area and washrooms clean and tidy
Stopped by for a late bite to eat. Service was fast., efficient And polite . Food was excellent.

Honestly the only McDonalds I like to sit down in. Its never very busy and the decor is more high class than your typical McDonalds. Classic one minute timing from paying to receiving your food as well.
TAKE A LOOK AT THE PICS THAT ARE POSTED MAKES ME FEEL LIKE THROWING UP    CAUSE I EAT THERE NEVER WILL AGAIN AND NEITHER SHOULD YOU...
One of the best made Skor McFlurrys Ive ever had! Drive-thru was also very quick!
Never had a problem. Rare for a mcdonalds location.
Liked the iced coffee
Very friendly, knowledgeable staff, quick service and there was no lineup when I went.
Best mc donalds I have been to in a very long time. All the food and drinks were perfect.
These guys provide my morning before work coffee - always cheerful and lovely, with hot predictable coffee!
Came here first time. Gagan helped me out with the order, excellent customer service. Will be back soon.
Always quick drive through service. $1.00 ice coffee ! Cant beat it.
A good place for a family meal, without breaking the bank. I like this location, although it is sometimes busy, it still feels cozy
The burgers were very yummy and the service was very quick too! (5 mins)
I go here a lot, and they always get my order right. Well managed.
This location had great service and the app worked flawlessly.
Quick and efficient.  No complaints.  Restaurant was clean and staff were friendly
good staff... drive thru moves quicker than most
They mess up your orders often and still have 5 stars because I love McDonalds!
I wish I remembered big boys name but he was a probably one of the happiest employees Ive ever dealt with.
Staff were friendly and tentative! Definitely the top one in Coquitlam.
They gave me lots of pickles on my double cheeseburger. That...is a five star rating in my book.
Beautiful people (outwardly and inwardly) work here.   I love them  like my own family
I love it not only because my brother and sister work there but the staff are awesome
Harpreet did great service :) :), always helpful and friendly staff
Always go here for quick bite.
I visited this Mc Donalds on crutches and after ordering I was unable to carry my try to the table and the staff instantly offered me help and helped bring my tay to the near by table.
Service was excellent, food tastey and its always very clean.
I visit during lunch and they never forget my extra sauce for my nuggets. 5/5
MY FAVORITE PLACE EVER!!!! NO REASON JUST LIKE IT
i go here all the time. drive through is the best
McDonald!!! Always good people take care of your family. Great service. Thank you
Fast and convenient place, thanks.
Since 1985, a big mac meal every few months, simply awesome.
Couldnt get my offer wasnt participated in this restaurant make sure you chek  before you come otherwise everything was good
Good one! Like all Mc Donalds!
More than half the time the orders wrong
Got the shamrock shake. Cant beat it.
Its a mcdonalds. But i cant live without coffee and its not bad for the price. 1$ right now!
Fast service, fresh food. Always happy here.
Fast, friendly service. Good food. Clean tables.
Little hidden but its McDonalds and you get what you expect
Go here for lunch every shift. Staff is very friendly
Quiet during later hours and good turn around time
Great fast food in town. And very clean.
Employees were really nice the young blonde manger was awesom
Try the junior chicken add thai sauce cant go wrong!
There is some parking.
Fast service even during the lunch time rush.
The salads they serve here are loaded with feta cheese, I couldnt even taste anything else!
Food was great but now I hate myself
Very clean mcd with good food
Excellent chocolate milkshake after hot day!
Great service from the guy at the window in the drive trough
Friendly staff, replaced incorrect items quickly!
Great Fillets Fish
They have great quality food McDonalds
Love the grand big mac.
nice and clean. not too busy I like
